A secure, lightweight, international Bitcoin wallet for Windows, MacOS and Linux

[[YourWallets.png]]

MultiBit makes performing Bitcoin transactions quick and simple

MultiBit comes in a variety of languages because Bitcoin is without borders

MultiBit is free and open source (MIT license).

MultiBit has a channel on YouTube to help you get started

##History

MultiBit was announced on September 12, 2011 (2.1).

